pageProduct.name: Swisse Ultibiotic Womens Flora Probiotic 30 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Ultibiotic Women's Flora Probiotic is a premium quality formula combining two clinically trialled strains-Lactobacillus rhamnosus (GR-1) and Lactobacillus reuteri (RC-14).

Swisse Ultibiotic Women’s Flora Probiotic is specifically formulated to:



  • Balance and maintain healthy vaginal microflora

  • Help support a healthy vaginal pH to reduce and relieve discomfort

  • Help temporarily reduce and relieve symptoms of mild vaginitis

  • Support and maintain urinary tract health.

Size: 30 Pack

Warnings

If pregnant or if symptoms persist, consult your healthcare practitioner.

IMPORTANT INFORMATION

No added lactose, gluten, yeast, egg, soy, artificial colours or artificial flavours.

Gluten free and dairy free.

Ingredients

EACH CAPSULE CONTAINS:
Lactobacillus rhamnosus (GR-1) 1.15 Billion CFU
Lactobacillus reuteri (RC-14) 1.15 Billion CFU

Directions

DIRECTIONS FOR USE - ADULT DOSAGE:
One capsule daily, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C.

Do not use if cap seal is broken.
